# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# AISA Club Website — Environment Variables
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# INSTRUCTIONS:
#   FOR LOCAL BUILD:
#     1. Copy this file → rename to ".env"
#     2. Fill in your values below
#     3. Run:  npm run build
#     4. Upload the generated "dist/" folder to Netlify
#
#   FOR NETLIFY AUTO-DEPLOY (recommended):
#     Go to: Netlify Dashboard → Your Site → Site Settings → Environment Variables
#     Add each variable below with its actual value.
#     Netlify will inject them automatically during every build.
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Supabase Project URL
# Found in: Supabase Dashboard → Project Settings → API → Project URL
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://YOUR_PROJECT_ID.supabase.co

# Supabase Anon / Public Key  (safe to expose in frontend)
# Found in: Supabase Dashboard → Project Settings → API → anon public
VITE_SUPABASE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...

# Supabase Service Role Key  ⚠️  KEEP THIS SECRET — never commit real value
# Found in: Supabase Dashboard → Project Settings → API → service_role secret
# Used only for admin-level operations (user management, RLS bypass)
VITE_SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...
